  title="Free roof inspection"
  subhead="Forty-photo packet. Written findings within 24 hours. No obligation, no pressure, no door-knocking."
  serviceTag="inspection"
>
  <h2>What's in the forty-photo packet</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Every slope — north, south, east, west — at roof level.</li>
    <li>Every valley, ridge, and penetration (pipe boots, vents, skylights, chimneys).</li>
    <li>Close-ups of any concerning finding (granule loss, hail impact, lift, nail pop, flashing).</li>
    <li>Attic photos if accessible — stains on decking, insulation moisture, ventilation issues.</li>
    <li>A plain-English written summary of condition + estimated remaining life.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Who this is for</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Homeowners</strong> — curious about roof age, planning to sell, or after a storm.</li>
    <li><strong>Real estate agents</strong> — pre-listing or during option period. Fast turnaround.</li>
    <li><strong>Insurance claimants</strong> — before an adjuster visit, so you know what to expect.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>What we don't do on an inspection call</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We don't give a verbal quote and leave. Estimate is written.</li>
    <li>We don't pressure a contract. If you need a repair or replacement, we'll follow up — you can ignore us forever.</li>
    <li>We don't knock doors. This call is because you booked it.</li>
  </ul>
</ServiceLayout>
